# UI primitives (admin SPA)

Before adding or editing form controls, modals, or card layouts in `apps/web`:

1. Read [`docs/frontend/component-inventory.md`](../../../docs/frontend/component-inventory.md).
2. Run or browse Storybook: `bun run --filter web storybook` from `personal-os-web/`.

## Use these primitives

| Need | Use |
|------|-----|
| Text input | `FormInput` from `@/components/atoms/FormInput` |
| Select | `Select` from `@/components/atoms/Select` |
| Textarea | `Textarea` from `@/components/atoms/Textarea` |
| Checkbox | `FormCheckbox` |
| Button | `Button` |
| Card panel | `Card` (+ `CardHeader` / `CardBody` / `CardFooter`) |
| Label + error | `FormField` |
| Modal | `Dialog` or `ConfirmDialog` |
| Mobile sheet | `BottomSheet` |
| Searchable select | `Combobox` / `MultiCombobox` |

Barrel imports: `@/components/atoms`, `@/components/molecules`.

## Do not

- Hand-roll raw `<select>`, `<textarea>`, or styled text `<input>` outside `components/atoms/` primitives.
- Hand-roll `fixed inset-0` modal overlays — use `Dialog`, `ConfirmDialog`, or `BottomSheet`.
- Copy the repeated card border class string — use `Card` or `cardSurfaceClassName`.
- Add a new one-off combobox — extend `Combobox` / `MultiCombobox` or wrap them.

ESLint (`custom/no-raw-form-control`, `custom/no-adhoc-modal`, `custom/prefer-card-primitive`) and `check-patterns` duplication ratchet enforce this. Ratchet baselines in `scripts/ui-duplication-baseline.json`.

## Create/Edit forms

When both `XCreateForm` and `XEditForm` exist for an entity, extract shared fields into `XFormFields` (see `BrandIdentityFormFields`, `GoalProgressWeightsFields`).
